<p class="byline-dateline"><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"  itemid="https://www.nytimes.com/by/dan-bilefsky">By <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/by/dan-bilefsky" title="More Articles by DAN BILEFSKY"><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="DAN BILEFSKY" itemprop="name" data-twitter-handle="DanBilefsky">DAN BILEFSKY</span></a></span><time class="dateline" datetime="2018-03-15T12:10:22-04:00" itemprop="dateModified" content="2018-03-15T12:10:22-04:00">MARCH 14, 2018</time>
